title: Tell Em Large Marge Trend Ya 2/23: Tiger Woods, Blade Force, DDOS, Mara Wilson, Jupiter
itunes:title: Tell Em Large Marge Trend Ya 2/23: Tiger Woods, Blade Force, DDOS, Mara Wilson, Jupiter
description:
On this edition of Tell Em Large Marge Trend Ya Jack and Miles discuss Tiger Woods getting in a car accident, Pakistan has introduced a new rollerblading Police force, a DDOS attack has taken down many servers as well as podcast publishing services, Mara Wilson speaks on child fame and trauma in relation to her life and Britney Spears, and new pictures of Jupiter have been released.
